                                    THIRD ANNOUNCEMENT

         CT2017: INTERNATIONAL CONFERENCE ON CATEGORY THEORY AND ITS APPLICATIONS

                                    July 16-22, 2017

                             University of British Columbia
                                   Vancouver, Canada

Dear Colleagues,

Registration is now open for CT2017. You may register and also reserve
accommodation through the PIMS website at

http://www.pims.math.ca/scientific-event/170716-c2ictc

Please book accommodation early because the room block set aside for CT2017 is
limited in size. There is also a special offer for a small block of dorm rooms
available for booking until March 1. Note that the deadline for early
registration is May 15.See the PIMS website for details.

This conference will be held on the University of British Columbia campus.
It will begin with a reception at 4pm on Sunday July 16, 2017, and will end
at 1pm on Saturday July 22, 2017. All those interested in category theory and
its applications are welcome.

Invited Speakers
D. Hofmann,
R. Lucyshyn-Wright
M. Menni
R. Pare
T. Van der Linden

We are pleased to announce a Special Invited Lecture at CT2017 by Bill
Lawvere.

Scientific Committee
M. M. Clementino
M. Gran
G. Janelidze(Chair)
P. T. Johnstone
J. L. MacDonald
S. Mantovani
R. H. Street
W. P. Tholen

Organizing Committee
M. Christiansen(Chair)
J. L. MacDonald
J. Picado

Abstracts may be submitted to ct2017@mat.uc.pt from now until May 31,
2017. Selection of speakers from these submissions will be made
shortly after that date.

A latex template for the abstracts has been included in the webpage with
address

http://www.mat.uc.pt/~ct2017

I hope to see many of you in Vancouver next summer.

Lauchie MacDonald



[For admin and other information see: http://www.mta.ca/~cat-dist/ ]

